blueprint.label: 1k SPM (harness)
blueprint.description:
This is a harness for
https://factorioprints.com/view/-LZY1wBZZ_C8xGihqShH
1k SPM all from raw.

To build:
- Place the construction site.
- Place this harness.
- Place the "1k SPM" blueprint from the above link so it overlaps the constant cobinators
- Turn on the construction site.
- Profit!

While it builds, add some more mines, too.  You'll need them.
